name: 2nd Edition of International Nutrition Research Webinar
content: Nutrition Virtual Research Webinar heartily welcomes the worldwide audience to participate within the conference that goes to be control in September 10-11, 2020\. Nutrition 2020 will focus and create an amazing interest in several application fields, as well as life sciences. The webinar aims to assemble leading educational scientists, professors and analysis students to exchange and share their experiences and research results on all aspects of Nutrition.
